{"tid":1393082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跪 求 立 即 出 動 解 放 軍","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T10:40:07.000Z","uid":35699,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1990f5b2d47ec8534f25a7339ce6b2082b2a0ea2","tid":1393082,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d583870fd950fd06a43c6cbfabc2530d48f49b","tid":1393082,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:25:05.000Z","msg":"Why?<br />\n<br />\n借po<br />\n<br />\n[文宣marketing]不如將「香港人日程表」個名upgrade下？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391245</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"43f5766c53981002d3d4c7a3567d5b0f40b6ec0b","tid":1393082,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"幫手推唔該  好緊急<br />\n[重要]  而家咁樣8月5會唔夠人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392774</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f4ad67ee5b7828478c0bbd1088aa155f56ffe5ec","tid":1393082,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:28:56.000Z","msg":"[緊急] 基督/天主教徒 禮賓府星期六要人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1393072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1393072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"855121f401f8f779b4786937a4dda81bf69dcf43","tid":1393082,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"解放軍唔會有膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ce892f0570c1d797f6baed8df37696475b04f3","tid":1393082,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"試下connect埋藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663c8d4c89d5dcaaf8598b816c1d8b1cedc77e57","tid":1393082,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:37:23.000Z","msg":"唔好直接比錢啦 買裝比佢地等佢地唔洗出自己錢買<br />\n佢地收左你錢 咪覺得唔衝對唔住你？<br />\n令佢地良心過得去唯一方法就係如果佢要裝我地就係前線擺低比佢 食就同平時一樣自己搞掂<br />\n<br />\n[個腦生屎？] 咪撚再講捐飯 、捐八達通  用下個腦啦 不服來辯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385666</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我相信香港人好醒目<br />\n所以我地應該從根本解決問題=買裝比前線 買完直接擺底就得 咁先最最最快最有效<br />\n唔好中計<br />\n帶頭吹風搞捐飯捐券捐錢全部都係<span style=\"color: red;\">鬼</span>，比d不知名人士（三毛藍絲）發國難財，仲要比<span style=\"color: red;\">警察有機會派人起我地既前線勇武義士底</span><br />\n<br />\n#香港人要醒目<br />\n#咪再講小朋友<br />\n#好多中年長者幫手<br />\n#唔係學生年輕人運動<br />\n#全民起義<br />\n#孤立不同年齡層係鬼係分化撚"},{"pid":"d3cffbf7ec7caa5cd32c7fd772f84479c594a4b0","tid":1393082,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5d583870fd950fd06a43c6cbfabc2530d48f49b","tid":1393082,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:25:05.000Z","msg":"Why?<br />\n<br />\n借po<br />\n<br />\n[文宣marketing]不如將「香港人日程表」個名upgrade下？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391245</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"維持治安，教廢青摺被"},{"pid":"354db3faa4afbb8759ec72054387d1e665fd7129","tid":1393082,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3cffbf7ec7caa5cd32c7fd772f84479c594a4b0","tid":1393082,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5d583870fd950fd06a43c6cbfabc2530d48f49b","tid":1393082,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:25:05.000Z","msg":"Why?<br />\n<br />\n借po<br />\n<br />\n[文宣marketing]不如將「香港人日程表」個名upgrade下？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391245</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"維持治安，教廢青摺被"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0